### GET all students
GET http://localhost:5000/students

### GET all student cases falling under query 'computing'
GET http://localhost:5000/students/search?query=computing

### GET all Students sorted by last updated
GET http://localhost:5000/students?sort=lastUpdated&order=desc&limit=20&page=2

### POST a new student
POST http://localhost:5000/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "caseId": "CASE-00123",
  "name": "Alice",
  "course": "Computing",
  "year": 2
}

